      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "……あ。おはようございます、{user}さん\n今、少しお時間いいですか？",
      "startTime": 4.2707405362,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 0.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、瑠依。オフは昨日までだったな\nでも、レッスンの予定時間より少し早いような……？",
      "startTime": 11.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、ちょっと早めに来ました\n{user}さんに渡したいものがあって……",
      "startTime": 18.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "これ、よろしければ\n先日のお土産です",
      "startTime": 23.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "名物の和菓子が美味しかったので、買ってきました\nお口に合えばいいんですけど",
      "startTime": 28.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、わざわざありがとう。いただくよ\nその様子だと、オフは楽しめたみたいだな",
      "startTime": 35.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "はい！\nおかげさまで、とてもリフレッシュ出来ました",
      "startTime": 39.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "本当に素敵な旅館だったんです\n風情があって、部屋からの景色も良くて",
      "startTime": 45.6349431931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "自然の音を聞きながら、ゆったりとくつろぐ……\nあんなに落ち着いた時間は、久しぶりでした",
      "startTime": 53.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それは良かった\nそういえばあの旅館、料理も美味しいって話だったけど",
      "startTime": 59.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですよ！\nお膳だと思ってたら、お鍋が出てきてビックリしました",
      "startTime": 65.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "旬の山菜や山芋を使ったお鍋だったんですけど\n味が染みててホクホクで、凄く美味しかったです",
      "startTime": 73.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "優から聞きましたけど、{user}さんが\n予約時に頼んでくれたんですよね？",
      "startTime": 81.1088225153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。選べるって言われたからな\nトリエルならこれだろう、って思ったんだ",
      "startTime": 86.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、さすがですね。私達としては大満足でした\nありがとうございました",
      "startTime": 94.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そうだ！　温泉も凄く良かったんですよ\n特に、露天風呂が",
      "startTime": 101.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "泊まった当日の夕方にも入ったんですけど\n朝風呂も気持ちいいって仲居さんに勧められて",
      "startTime": 108.2927223245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに朝は空気が冷たかったんですけど\nお湯に浸かった瞬間、本当に気持ち良くて……",
      "startTime": 115.745216636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、朝の露天風呂は一気に目が覚めるし\n気持ちいいよなぁ……",
      "startTime": 123.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "はい。立ち上る湯気がキラキラしてて\n夕方のお風呂とはまた違った趣がありましたね",
      "startTime": 129.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "時間帯が違うだけで、景色も音も\n空気の香りすらも違うんだなって思いました",
      "startTime": 137.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "思い返せば私、朝の露天風呂ってあれが初めてで\nいい体験が出来たなって思います",
      "startTime": 146.8472756849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。めずらしく瑠依が饒舌になるほどだから\n本当に満喫出来たんだろうな",
      "startTime": 155.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "あ……\nそ、そう……かもしれません……けど",
      "startTime": 159.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "うう……ちょっとはしゃぎ過ぎたかも\n忘れて下さい……",
      "startTime": 166.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui020.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも！\nただリフレッシュしただけじゃありませんから",
      "startTime": 170.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui021.m4a",
      "text": "優やすみれとも、今後の目標を改めて確認出来た\n有意義な時間になりましたし",
      "startTime": 178.0366916383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今後の目標か……\n俺にも聞かせてくれるか？",
      "startTime": 182.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui022.m4a",
      "text": "もう、逃げ腰にはなりません\n変に守りの姿勢を取ったりもしません",
      "startTime": 187.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui023.m4a",
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリでサニピに負けて\nI-UNITYでどん底を味わって……",
      "startTime": 194.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui024.m4a",
      "text": "それ以来、いかに自分達が挑戦を恐れていたのか\n今回の件で痛感しました",
      "startTime": 202.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui025.m4a",
      "text": "言葉では常に上を向いていたつもりだったのに\n心のどこかで、ずっと逃げていたんだなって",
      "startTime": 208.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依達の気持ちを考えれば、仕方ないことだったと思う\n……けど確かに、臆病になっていたかもしれないな",
      "startTime": 217.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui026.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そんなのはやっぱり、私達らしくない\nファンのみんなも、こんな私達を望んではいない",
      "startTime": 225.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui027.m4a",
      "text": "なら、私達はこれから\n常に挑戦者であるべきだって思ったんです",
      "startTime": 232.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_07_03-rui028.m4a",
